overview: This show captures the complete concert that Los Gatos Salvajes offered, celebrating the 40th Anniversary of its creation. The concert preserves the chronological list of songs that they perform, having chosen the best shots of the shows held on July 29 and 30 at the ND Ateneo Theater and on August 12 and 13 at the La Comedia Theater in Rosario.
title: Los Gatos Salvajes: En concierto 2005
